item.content:encoded:
Are you ready for a party? It’s been a while since these princesses went out at a party and they are so excited to finally go out and have some fun! By the way, what do teens wear at parties nowadays? What would you wear, if you were to go out at this killer party tonight? Can you help these princesses get ready and look fabulous? Open their wardrobe and start to mix and match some cute and funky tops with skirts, pants, or shorts and find some trendy accessories. Have fun!

item.content:encoded:
Toy-Match is a matching-3 game. You can be relaxed in this game. The mission is to collect some directional things. It is easy, just match three or more same color blocks to a line. If you match the blocks with the background, it will collect them. When you collect all the props, you can continue the next level. But your moves are limited, you should better collect them before running out of moves. Sounds difficult? Do not be upset, we will mention you if you actually do not know how to move. Let us enjoy the game!
Click to play.

item.content:encoded:
Egg Age is a relaxing matching-3 game. Have you seen eggs of dinosaurs?Today is your chance, you will see many kinds of dinosaur eggs in this game! Each level will give your goals, you have to match eggs to collect the pointed eggs. When you get enough eggs then you can continue the next level. But the moves are limited, you should complete the mission before move run out. Some eggs can help you vanish lots of eggs, be patient to think about it. How to use fewer moves to get more eggs?

Jessie is a fashion girl. She loves getting her nails done and has a DIY nail SPA room at her own home. Take care of her nails with her, apply a mask, trim them, file them, polish them, and have fun getting them done. Experiment with different nail polish and patterns and find the best accessories for her. Before you decorate her nails, do a nail spa. Make sure they are clean and tidy that can make sure Fingernail pieces decorate fluently.

Ice princess in the game is very personalized.Ice princess doesn’t like traditional and conservative long skirts, she likes fashionable shorts. Players can choose clothes with various patterns for ice princess, including beautiful girl soldiers, cats and dogs, stars and butterflies,and so on. In addition, players can also choose different hair styles for ice princess. Snow white hair can reflect the temperament of ice princess more, blue hair can experience the personality of ice princess more, no matter what color of hair, players can enjoy the beautiful game.

item.content:encoded:
Foodtycoon Frvr is a good managing game. Owning a coffee shop is every girl’s dream, now it comes true! You are mastering a little coffee shop, learn how to manage it, and how the shop keeps running well. I will teach you how to make drinks, with your level up you could make more kinds of drinks. Customers will get more and more, their Purchase demand is also more strange, but you have to satisfy them. You will get busier, improve your equipment to cook faster, you can also upgrade the materials that earn more money! Collect keys to unlock more characters!
Click to cook
